Metadata: University of California Sea Grant Extension Program

Tidelines will be published quarterly as a local newsletter dealing with practical problems in the areas of Commercial and sport fisheries; Seafood processing, aquaculture, marine education and youth programs, marine research, waterfront management, boating industry, marine transportation, environmental policy, and coastal engineering. Cover articles include: Clean boating tips, Hazardous waste disposal information, Lightning protections for boats, Enjoy raw seafood safely, Marinas go blue! Fishermen speak out, Pleasure boat maintenance tips!
